skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crazy haiku
des: Crazy Haiku is a simple skill that contains a list of short entertaining poems which were designed to brighten up your day. You can start this skill by saying "Alexa, open crazy haiku" and then, "Ask crazy haiku to read me a poem" or "Tell crazy haiku to read me something" to see what it has up its sleeve ;)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
